parameters: \n<Blood Maid>It really pains me to see her like this...\.\.\.I'm new around here but all the other maids say she was completely different when she was in the Hole.\.\. If only she'd get better...\.\.\.
\n<Blood Maid>But surely,\. one day it will happen.\.\. She can weather any storm,\. and it's our job to stay by her side until she does.\.\.
\n<Blood Maid>Lady Anzu will recover soon!\.\. I just know it!\.\. I believe in her!\.\.
\n<Blood Maid>And when she does,\. the mansion should be completely clean.\.\. Not a speck of dust to be seen anywhere!\.\.
\n<Blood Maid>I'm sure it'll make her feel even better if that happens.\.\.
\n<Blood Maid>Lady Anzu will recover soon!\.\. I just know it!\.\. I believe in her!\.\.
\n<Blood Maid>And when she does,\. the mansion should be completely clean.\.\. Not a speck of dust to be seen anywhere!\.\.
\n<Blood Maid>I'm sure it'll make her feel even better if that happens.\.\.
\n<Blood Maid>What are you doing here?!\.\. Our Lady is very weak,\. you're not allowed past here!
\n<Blood Maid>Long are the days when she would be active and cheerful,\. full of energy down in the Hole where she had free access to better quality mana.\.\.
\n<Blood Maid>The kind of quality mana that a noble like her deserves.\.\.
\n<Blood Maid>Until she recovers,\. I'm afraid she's in no condition to receive guests.\.\.
\n<???>What makes you think you can just step in our Lady's Manor?\.\. You are...\.\.\. an interesting and clueless being,\. aren't you?
\n<\n[1]>Leave me alone!\.\. I have to meet the leader of this place!
\n<\n[1]>I have to go down the Hole!
\n<???>Careful what you wish for,\. cursed one.\.\. \BST[3]Whatever you're looking for,\. it's already lost.
\n<\n[1]>You're ticking me off!!\.\. Go tell that Lady of yours to come out,\. I've got no time to lose with you!
\n<???>\c[18]Lady Anzu\c[0]...\.\.\. is not well right now,\. I'm afraid.\.\. You should come back at another time,\. kitten.
\n<\n[1]>Hmph!\.\. Yea,\. go away,\. see if I care.
